OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News producer Lauren
OL,7,FBaulch
OL,9,FIt was the hacking group linked to
OL,10,Fboth the M&S and Co-op cyber attacks,
OL,11,Fbut it appears Scattered Spider has a
OL,12,Fnew sector in its sights.
OL,14,FInitially targeting retail companies,
OL,15,Fthe group now appears to be setting
OL,16,Fits sights on the aviation industry.
OL,18,FIn the US, the Federal Bureau of
OL,19,FInvestigation recently posted on the
OL,20,Fsocial media platform X, raising the
OL,21,Falarm.
