OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FBoth Google and the US cybersecurity
OL,7,Fcompany Palo Alto Networks have also
OL,8,Fwarned of the potential threat.
OL,10,FIn a statement posted on LinkedIn, Sam
OL,11,FRubin of Palo Alto said that the
OL,12,Fcompany has "observed Muddled Libra
OL,13,F(also known as Scattered Spider)
OL,14,Ftargeting the aviation industry".
