OL,6,FGoogle experts reported similar
OL,7,Ffindings. Charles Carmakal, an
OL,8,Fexecutive for Google's cybersecurity
OL,9,Funit, said the company was "aware of
OL,10,Fmultiple incidents in the airline and
OL,11,Ftransportation sector which resemble
OL,12,Fthe operations of UNC3944 or Scattered
OL,13,FSpider".
OL,15,FNo references were made to any
OL,16,Fspecific airlines, but recently
OL,17,FCanadian airline WestJet, Hawaiian
OL,18,FAirlines and Qantas have all suffered
OL,19,Ffrom cyber attacks.
