OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FThe airlines have not released any
OL,7,Fdetails on potential links between the
OL,8,Fincidents and Scattered Spider, but
OL,9,Fthe hacking group has been blamed for
OL,10,Fsome of the most disruptive hacks
OL,11,Facross the UK and US in recent memory.
OL,13,FWho are Scattered Spider?
OL,15,FAccording to America's Cyber Defence
OL,16,FAgency, Scattered Spider is a
OL,17,Fcybercriminal group that targets large
OL,18,Fcompanies and their IT help desks.
