OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FScattered Spider members have
OL,7,Ftypically engaged in data theft for
OL,8,Fextortion and have been known to use
OL,9,FBlackCat/ALPHV ransomware.
OL,11,FThe group initially dabbled in
OL,12,Ffinancial fraud and social media
OL,13,Fhacking but has become more advanced,
OL,14,Fconducting data breaches and stealing
OL,15,Fcryptocurrency.
OL,17,FSome of its members are as young as 16
OL,18,Fyears old and meet on hacking forums,
OL,19,Fdiscord servers and Telegram channels.
OL,21,FWhy the aviation sector?
