OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FITV News spoke to cyber security
OL,7,Fexpert Graham Cluley about the reasons
OL,8,Fwhy the aviation sector is likely on
OL,9,Fthe target list.
OL,11,F"Airlines and firms in the aviation
OL,12,Findustry consist of an attractive
OL,13,Fcocktail of critical infrastructure,
OL,14,Fsometimes outdated tech, and massive
OL,15,Fcustomer databases that can prove
OL,16,Firresistible to hackers," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
