OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,F"Many aviation industry businesses
OL,7,Fstill rely on legacy systems bolted
OL,8,Fonto newer platforms, which determined
OL,9,Fhackers like Scattered Spider love to
OL,10,Fexploit.
OL,12,F"Plus, of course, with the summer
OL,13,Fholidays about to begin and many
OL,14,Ftravellers planning to jet overseas,
OL,15,Fhackers will view that as a greater
OL,16,Fincentive than ever for airlines to
OL,17,Fpay up, rather than cause chaos for
OL,18,Ftheir customers."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
