OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,FMr Cluley said airlines need to harden
OL,7,Ftheir defences to prevent attacks like
OL,8,Fthis from happening.
OL,10,F"Many hackers break into systems via
OL,11,Fstolen or phished credentials," he
OL,12,Fexplained.
OL,14,F"Scattered Spider, for instance, has
OL,15,Foften used the ploy of posing as
OL,16,Femployees who have been locked out of
OL,17,Ftheir accounts, and tricking service
OL,18,Fdesks into giving them access.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
