OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F312A1751628484
OL,3,CCould airlines be the new target for
OL,4,Chacking group Scattered Spider?
OL,6,F"Additionally, the air industry needs
OL,7,Fto keep a close eye on its third-party
OL,8,Fsuppliers - especially those which
OL,9,Fhave privileged access to its network
OL,10,For data. Supply chain attacks are a
OL,11,Ffavourite amongst hackers."
OL,13,F"Hopefully businesses in the air
OL,14,Findustry are also 'hacking themselves'
OL,15,F- in other words, simulating the
OL,16,Fmethods used by hackers to find
OL,17,Fweaknesses in their systems before
OL,18,Fthey are exploited by cybercriminals,"
OL,19,Fhe continued.
