OL,6,F"Finally, there's a lot to be said for
OL,7,Fstaff training - educating them about
OL,8,Fhow hackers trick staff into making
OL,9,Fmistakes that can result in a cyber
OL,10,Fattack succeeding."
OL,12,FAs a customer, it's important to
OL,13,Fensure you have the best measures in
OL,14,Fplace to protect yourself if an
OL,15,Fairline is targeted.
OL,17,F"It's the airline that gets hacked,
OL,18,Fnot you," Mr Cluley said. "But it
OL,19,Fmight be your data that ends up in the
OL,20,Fhands of cybercriminals".
