OL,6,FHe recommends using unique, strong
OL,7,Fpasswords and advises customers not to
OL,8,Fuse the same password for different
OL,9,Fplaces on the internet.
OL,11,F"Where possible, enable multi-factor
OL,12,Fauthentication (also known sometimes
OL,13,Fas two-factor authentication)," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FHe also said that paying with a credit
OL,17,Fcard makes it easier to get your money
OL,18,Fback if fraud occurs.
