OL,6,FHe added: "You may also be wise to use
OL,7,Fa 'virtual card' which has a lower
OL,8,Fspending limit on it or can be locked
OL,9,Fto a specific merchant.
OL,11,F"Some banks offer this facility -
OL,12,Fmaking it possible to create a unique
OL,13,Fcard number that is linked to your
OL,14,Freal account but cannot be reused
OL,15,Felsewhere. If a travel site or airline
OL,16,Fis breached, your actual credit card
OL,17,Fnumber isn't exposed."
